Description: For sale is a USA made Fender Vintage Hot Rod '52 Telecaster - black. This guitar has been used but not abused. It’s in great shape without any serious issues, modifications or repairs. The finish and the case display some wear and tear such as pick marks and some light buckle rash on the back. A small piece of the lacquer finish paint chipped away at the neck pocket (see pic). This is a very common occurrence for Fenders and is one of those things that just happens. You can either apply some black finger nail polish or color the bare wood with a black sharpie. I decided to leave it alone as it doesn't affect the tone or playability of the instrument. The frets are in excellent shape and display only the very slightest hint of the beginnings of wear. No deep ruts or anything. This is a NO RESERVE auction! Shipping to USA and Canada is $49.00 USD.
